last train to &lt;unk&gt; is a 1999 indian hindi suspense thriller film written and directed by anurag kashyap . the film stars anurag kashyap , kay kay menon , anupam kher , anurag kashyap , kay kay menon , anupam kher , anurag kashyap , kay kay menon , anupam kher , anurag kashyap , kay kay menon , anupam kher , anurag kashyap , kay kay menon and pooja sharma in the lead roles . the film won the special jury award at the 8th annual indian screen awards .